# MIGRATION CHECKLIST: 1) bun add pg @types/pg  2) Change prisma provider to postgresql
# 3) bunx prisma migrate dev --name init-postgresql  4) bunx prisma db seed
# 5) Remove output: "standalone" if not using Vercel  6) bun run test
